blocks.subject: NYMEX PRODUCT LIST FOR OTC CLEARING
text: Friends:
The NYMEX is preparing to commence trading of OTC cleared contracts beginning
May 20.  As a clearing customer of BNP Paribas Commodity Futures you will have
the ability to clear these OTC cleared products in your account with us.
The attached file lists the products that will be available on May 20.  Please
call us with questions in New York at 212-841-3333 or in London at
Thank You,
BNP Paribas Commodity Futures, Inc.
This message and any attachments (the "message") is
intended solely for the addressees and is confidential.
If you receive this message in error, please delete it and
immediately notify the sender. Any use not in accord with

or partial, is prohibited except formal approval. The internet

BNP PARIBAS (and its subsidiaries) shall (will) not
therefore be liable for the message if modified.
